<p>This thing makes Thaumiel an esoteric class, which it really always was before it became more mainstream and people wanted to use it without feeling like they're using an esoteric class. Obviously there is no canon etc etc, but in the canon of this document Thaumiel is esoteric again.</p>
<p>Also, Threat Levels aren't really a thing, and they're really vague. If you read this document and the component page, you'll see that they're given specific (but flexible) parameters.</p>

